headline: Cognizant and Typeface Partner to Modernize Enterprise Marketing Through Agentic AI Orchestration
summary: Cognizant (NASDAQ: CTSH) and Typeface today announced a strategic partnership to help enterprises modernize marketing operations through agentic AI orchestration. By combining Cognizant's global delivery and transformation services with Typeface's marketing platform, the companies will transform fragmented workflows into connected, efficient and scalable marketing processes.
